# Only `site/` is needed for the landing-page Dockerfile build.
# Excluding everything else makes the build context tiny + avoids
# broken symlinks in examples/ (point at a sibling repo not in CI).
**

# Allow back in only what site/Dockerfile actually needs:
!site/
!site/**

# Always exclude the build output (we generate it inside the image)
site/_site/

# Hygiene
**/.DS_Store
**/node_modules/
**/.git/
